{"tid":577675,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[希特拉,李+x ,維尼帝]美歌手複製亡犬捱轟","createTime":"2018-03-02T03:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T03:31:57.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b10d577f31f3f68d3893d03572a7b3e625059944","tid":577675,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T03:14:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180302/57889858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180302%2F57889858&d=tzihyB9kHcV2KeLkcst4spUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=ac826755\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180302%2F57889858&h=98323624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180302/57889858</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國75歲老牌歌手芭芭拉史翠珊（Barbra Streisand）去年遭受喪犬之痛，她趁愛犬死前安排好將牠複製，成功複製出兩隻狗。<br />\n<br />\n芭芭拉史翠珊的14歲愛犬「Samantha」去年去世，她在愛犬死前安排複製公司的職員，從牠的口及胃抽取細胞。職員利用這些細胞，成功利用複製技術複製出兩隻狗狗。在等候複製狗誕生前，芭芭拉史翠珊又領養了「Samantha」的遠親。<br />\n兩隻複製狗分別名為「Miss Scarlett」及「Miss Violet」，芭芭拉史翠珊為牠們穿上相應顏色的衣服，以茲識別。雖然兩隻狗外貌都與「Samantha」一模一樣，但牠們的性格卻截然不同。芭芭拉史翠珊說：「我正等牠們再長大一點，好等我可以看看牠們有沒有牠的棕色眼睛，以及牠的嚴肅態度。」<br />\n複製狗狗耗費不菲，以美國複製公司ViaGen為例，複製一隻狗就索價3.6萬英鎊（約38.7萬港元）。有愛護動物團體批評，芭芭拉史翠珊斥巨資複製狗狗其實無助愛犬「長生不老」，只是製造一隻完全<br />\n<br />\n長肛生物科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e17ebf44bf83dc482acb56e24d56a1159af18a3","tid":577675,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T03:25:49.000Z","msg":"替代品"},{"pid":"3de78902a96b0c2cf2d661e4c6847d3ebf9e4be0","tid":577675,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0